quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,Kodi iwe wamuona amene amabwerera m’mbuyo
  53,34,Amene adapereka pang’ono ndipo anasiya kupereka
  53,35,Kodi iye amadziwa za zinthu zobisika kuti akhoza kuziona
  53,36,Kodi kapena iye sadauzidwe za mawu amene ali m’mabuku a Mose
  53,37,Ndiponso za Abrahamu amene adakwaniritsa malamulo
  53,38,Kuti palibe munthu amene adzasenza katundu wa mnzake
  53,39,Ndipo kuti munthu sadzapeza chilichonse kupatula chimene wachigwirira ntchito
  53,40,Ndipo kuti ntchito zake zidzaoneka
  53,41,Pamenepo iye adzalipidwa malipiro ake oyenera
  53,42,Ndipo kuti kwa Ambuye wanu ndi kumene nonse mudzapita
  53,43,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amawachititsa anthu kuseka ndi kuwaliritsa
  53,44,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"Ndiponso kuti Iye adalenga zinthu ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi"
  53,46,Kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene umatuluka
  53,47,Ndipo kuti kwa Iye kuli chilengedwe chachiwiri
  53,48,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka chuma ndi chisangalalo
  53,49,Ndipo kuti Iye ndiye Ambuye wa nyenyezi yamphamvu yotchedwa Sirius
  53,50,Kuti ndiye amene adaononga anthu akale a mphamvu kwambiri a mtundu wa a Aad kale
  53,51,Ndi anthu a mtundu wa a Thamoud. Ndipo Iye sadasiye wina aliyense
  53,52,Ndi anthu a Nowa amakedzana ndithudi iwo adali osalungama ndi oswa malamulo mwamwano
  53,53,Ndipo iye adaononga mizinda yomwe idali yogonjetsedwa
  53,54,Kotero iwo adawavundikira nd chimene chidawavundikira
  53,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wako zimene udzazikayikira
  53,56,Uyu ndi mchenjezi wotsatizana ndi achenjezi a makedzana
  53,57,Tsiku louka kwa akufa lili pafupi
  53,58,Palibe wina kupatula Mulungu amene akhoza kulipherera
  53,59,Kodi inu mulikudabwa pa zimene zili kulakatulidwa
  53,60,Ndipo inu muli kuseka m’malo mwakulira
  53,61,Ndi kumapitirizabe kuchita zinthu zopanda pake
  53,62,Motero gunditsani nkhope zanu pansi ndipo pembedzani Mulungu mmodzi yekha